Working Area: (before add .)
git clean -n -d: dry run (preview)(untracked files and directories, which are going to be deleted from working area)
git clean -f -d: forcefully delete the untracked files and directories, which are in working area



Staging Area: (before commit)
git restore
git restore --stagged


Local Repo: (after commit) && (before push)
git reset --soft HEAD~1: commit will be delted, but files are staged.
git reset --hard HEAD~1: everything will be deleted till last commit.


